msgid "Please save and pin your key on the clipboard as it is saved in the browser you use only. If you changed browsers, you'll need to enter it again."
msgstr "Harap simpan dan pin token Anda di clipboard karena hanya tersimpan di browser yang Anda gunakan. Jika Anda mengganti browser, Anda perlu memasukkannya lagi."

#: templates/api.html:63
msgid "How can I return to use the tool Token:"
msgstr "Bagaimana cara kembali menggunakan Token alat:"

#: templates/api.html:66
msgid "Delete your key from the page here or delete the site cookies"
msgstr "Hapus token Anda dari halaman ini atau hapus cookie situs"

#: templates/api.html:69
msgid "Would the tool use my Token for other users:"
msgstr "Apakah alat ini akan menggunakan Token saya untuk pengguna lain:"

#: templates/api.html:72
msgid "No, your Token is saved in your cookies not in a DB"
msgstr "Tidak, Token Anda tersimpan di cookie Anda, bukan di DB"

#: templates/api.html:74
msgid "How secure will be the Token?"
msgstr "Seberapa aman Token ini?"

#: templates/api.html:77
msgid "We are not setting the Token directly to the cookie. Instead, we are generating a token based on your Token which expires in every one hour then it regenerates a new token automatically. So you can say your Token is super secured."
msgstr "Web tidak menyimpan Token secara langsung di cookie. Sebaliknya, web menghasilkan token berdasarkan Token Anda yang kedaluwarsa setiap satu jam, lalu menghasilkan token baru secara otomatis. Jadi bisa dibilang Token Anda sangat aman."

